%o A213503 (SageMath) [[(n-k+1)*((n-k+1)^3 + 4*(n-k+1)^2*k + 6*k*(n-k+1) - n + 3*k - 1)/12 for k in (1..n)] for n in (1..12)] # _G. C. Greubel_, Jul 05 2019
